<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_Airlines_Flight_175" title="United Airlines Flight 175">United Airlines Flight 175</a>, which had been taken over by hijackers, hits the South Tower of the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_Trade_Center_(1973%E2%80%932001)" title="World Trade Center (1973â€“2001)">World Trade Center</a> during <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/September_11_attacks" title="September 11 attacks">September 11 attacks</a> in 2001, in <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_York_City" title="New York City">New York City</a>.</div>
